                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-268-off1535 t18200918-268-cd1536"></join>, 24 pieces of velveteen, value 20 s., and 30 buttons, value 9 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-268-victim2498" type="victimName">
                           Daniel 
